  "description": "A wide-angle shot depicts a bustling waterfront scene with a prominent bridge in the background. The foreground features a wooden pier with multiple pilings supporting a walkway, and various metal structures, potentially part of a dock or loading facility. A tall, slender pole with attached equipment stands out near the left edge. In the distance, a large suspension bridge with multiple towers and cables stretches across the water, connecting to a hazy cityscape on the far shore. Several boats and ships are visible in the water. The sky is clear and a vibrant blue. A seagull is perched atop the pole. The overall impression is one of a working port with the bridge serving as a landmark.",
